message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as it deals with signal processing and analysis. cs.SD is followed by cs.SI (social and information networks) as the paper deals with classification of audio signals. cs.CV (computer vision and pattern recognition) is also a possible category as the paper uses CNNs for feature extraction. cs.LG (machine learning) and cs.CL (computation and language) are also possible categories as the paper uses SVM for classification and deals with audio signal processing.
